.Dd January 19, 2017
.Dt SCHED_GETCPU 2
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm sched_getcpu
.Nd get the CPU on which the calling thread is running
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libc
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In sys/types.h
.In sys/sched.h
.Ft int
.Fn sched_getcpu "void"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn sched_getcpu
returns the CPU on which the calling thread is running.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr usched_set 2
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Fn sched_getcpu
function first appeared in
.Dx 4.7 .
